"<guilabel>Round</guilabel> and <guilabel>Square</guilabel> (the default). "
"Diamond and Round shapes will only be visible when you lower <guilabel>Size "
"Ratio X/Y</guilabel> to about 0.6 (Diamond) or 0.5 (Round)."
